wn, eclipsing Henderson by a minute and a half.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\", \"score\": 0.9999998166749887, \"rank\": 8.964495542197147e-08, \"text\": \"Henderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long road\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"runner-up\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"World Championships\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"a league\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British rider was in fact something of a latecomer to cycling, and excelled as a national champion in skiing as a youngster, which perhaps helped her stay upright in treacherous conditions.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9941834189818226, \"rank\": 0.003535846725079156, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"a latecomer\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"a national champion\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"skiing\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"a youngster\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"treacherous conditions\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not realise how slippery it was out there until I was already on the course,\\\" Henderson said afterwards.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\", \"score\": 0.9999998166749887, \"rank\": 8.964495542197147e-08, \"text\": \"Henderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Henderson_Jr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought 'I could lose the whole Olympic Games in one corner here' and you gain all your time in the straights.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole Olympic Games\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"one corner\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"all your time\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the straights\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I really took control and my coach did a really good job to keep me calm the whole way through.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good job\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole way\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last year I was two seconds from the bronze in worlds so I am really happy to be on the right side of the seconds this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two seconds\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"worlds\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1197}, {