elongated \\\"f**k\\\".\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2190, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.8821623645709302, \"rank\": 0.09238847861737459, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowd\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mew Jensen and Harper still had three more dives to watch before the medal was confirmed - and when it was, the pair leapt and hugged their coaching staff.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mew Jensen\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"Harper\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"three more dives\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"their coaching staff\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They now have an Olympic medal to match their bronze at last year's World Championships.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"their bronze\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's World Championships\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mew Jensen said: \\\"We knew that even after our last dive that we would still be on the back foot and we knew that Australia needed to mess up.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.8768464770900912, \"rank\": 0.12192787031213358, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org